<i>who uploads his consciousness</i>

19:48.086 --> 19:51.023
<i>into a tall, agile creature</i>

19:51.089 --> 19:52.724
<i>that lives in some kind of</i>

19:52.791 --> 19:54.660
<i>jungle paradise</i>

19:54.726 --> 19:57.329
<i>where they even speak</i>
<i>their own language</i>

