21:01.660 --> 21:04.196
Wilson:
<i>After a while, they started</i>
<i>to say a bunch of stuff</i>

21:04.262 --> 21:06.531
<i>that you didn't</i>
<i>really understand.</i>

21:06.598 --> 21:09.668
(speaking Na'vi)

21:12.738 --> 21:13.705
(laughs)

