Wilson:
<i>And you quickly realize that</i>

21:15.941 --> 21:19.444
<i>it was actually</i>
<i>the language from the movie,</i>

21:19.511 --> 21:21.580
<i>which they all spoke fluently.</i>

21:21.647 --> 21:24.016
The reason that the adjective
has to be next to the word

21:24.082 --> 21:27.119
that it describes is because
