I saw it the first two times
in theaters, and I was like,

22:03.055 --> 22:05.223
this is one of the best
movies I've ever seen.

22:05.290 --> 22:07.259
I like, love this movie.

22:07.325 --> 22:09.761
Every time I've
watched it after,

22:11.029 --> 22:14.199
I had-- I would always
hit about a week or two

22:14.266 --> 22:17.402
-of a really deep depression.
