22:17.469 --> 22:19.838
wow, like, this is so beautiful,

22:19.905 --> 22:22.841
and it also, also just
feels impossible.

22:22.908 --> 22:24.976
Like, this can never be.

22:25.043 --> 22:27.479
That's where the hopelessness
component comes from.

22:27.546 --> 22:30.849
Fan 4:
