depression hit hard

22:30.916 --> 22:33.785
because I had this
serial track record

22:33.852 --> 22:37.289
of just trying to escape
my reality, and,

22:37.355 --> 22:38.790
uh, it--

22:38.857 --> 22:41.927
"Avatar" provided
that escapism in a way

22:41.993 --> 22:45.397
that I had never really
experienced before.

22:45.464 --> 22:48.233
If you could lay down tonight,

22:48.300 --> 22:52.204
and wake up tomorrow
as a Na'vi on Pandora...

22:52.270 --> 22:54.239
-Heck yes!
