I just couldn't see my life
going anywhere,

23:38.150 --> 23:40.252
and I was honestly
experiencing

23:40.318 --> 23:43.221
a lot of suicidal ideation,

23:43.288 --> 23:46.224
and I just started talking

23:46.291 --> 23:49.261
to some of the people
on Learn Na'vi,

23:49.327 --> 23:52.197
